{"tid":2176750,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 中資藍店Pizza Express喺炒office人個email自認藍!","createTime":"2020-08-27T09:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T17:07:08.000Z","uid":279513,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5cf5c1caddcecbbb17f59ae8be9591b3bac7d1","tid":2176750,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:29:27.000Z","msg":"Pizza Express全球店其實都係中資聯想其下嘅Hony Capital全資擁有嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PizzaExpress\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FPizzaExpress&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=8e308a9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PizzaExpress</a><br />\n<br />\n話說武漢肺炎英國Pizza Express都好撚唔掂<br />\n要執英國15%舖，炒1100人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/business-53830064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-53830064&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=79cb4456\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-53830064&h=f50cbf7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/business-53830064</a><br />\n<br />\n咁香港都唔例外，呢幾日就出左個email話炒人啦<br />\n但明明生意差係因為武漢肺炎，但佢就話舊年social events喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但最奇怪係生意差要炒人但佢哩幾日會喺北角開新舖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n北角手足記得唔好新屎坑幫襯佢呀<br />\n<br />\n而Pizza Express唔知點解喺Wolipay等等app係冇mark做藍店嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇手足可以mark返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家記得尖沙咀間 新辣道 都係佢集團其下<br />\nDeliveroo入面Pasta Project都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a971257fd717a2f8